          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Si detector with an area of 2000 mm2 and a",
                " thickness of 300 mu-m was used. In the case of the",
                " forward 15 MeV measurement, a thicker detector",
                " (2 mm/1250 mm2) was mounted."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The energy calibration of the surface barrier",
                " detector was performed with the help of a Th-228",
                " alpha-source, yielding peaks with energies between",
                " 5.4 and 8.8 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets were deuterated polyethylene foils: a",
                " CD-2 foil has a weight of 4.88 (0.09)mg/cm**2, a",
                " CH-2 foil - 4.56 (0.03) mg/cm**2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Statistical errors. For the extreme angles,",
                " the statistical error on the results amounts 4-5% (at",
                " 0 degr.) and 7-8 % (180 degr.), respectively,",
                " while the systematic uncertainty was at most 3 %."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-SYS",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Systematic uncertainties were estimated",
                " to be not more than 3% for the following sources:",
                " - bremsstrahlung shape;",
                " - beam monitoring;",
                " - target thickness;",
                " - geometry effects;",
                " - analysis (energy loss, multiple scattering, etc.)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 0, and 180 degree, as well as the 90 degree",
                " differential cross sections for the 2H(gamma,p)n",
                " reaction have been measured at lab photon energies",
                " between 7 and 19 MeV. Special attention was paid to",
                " the accuracy, in particular by measuring the forward",
                " Compton electron yield. The data confirm the",
                " existence of a minimum in the forward cross section",
                " and indicate beyond any doubt that the fore/aft ratio",
                " is larger than unity. Comparison shows reasonable",
                " agreement with the results from recent \"conventional\"",
                " theoretical approaches, including meason exchange and",
                " relativistic corrections, although the description of",
                " the C-coefficient, appearing in the Partovi expansion",
                " of the differential cross section, remains",
                " unsatisfactory. A possible source for this",
                " discrepancy could be the inadequate description of",
                " the E1 and/or the E2 transition operator."
              ]
            }
          ],
